# TASK 3 - IMAGE CAPTIONING AI

## Description
This project generates captions for images using Artificial Intelligence. It uses the BLIP (Bootstrapping Language-Image Pre-training) model from Hugging Face to analyze an image and create a descriptive caption automatically.

## Features
- Generates captions for images
- Uses a pre-trained deep learning model
- Simple and easy-to-understand Python code

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Transformers
- PyTorch
- Pillow

